        <mxCell id="step-1-desc-legend" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=14;labelBackgroundColor=none;whiteSpace=wrap;fontFamily=Helvetica;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Producers &amp;rarr; MSK (3+ consumers)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0,0,0), rgb(255,255,255));&quot;&gt;With 3+ consumer apps, MSK at $933/mo beats Kinesis EFO at $2,160/mo (5 consumers x 20 shards). Break-even at ~3 consumers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1" parent="step-1-legend">
